<dl id="n38008b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n38" href="#n38008b">N38 (VI.B.32)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n38all.htm#n38008b"> 8(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">H</font> ballast office / ball falls </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: The Ballast Office, at the corner of Westmoreland Street and Aston Quay, had a ball on a pole which fell each day at 1 pm Greenwich Mean Time. </mm> </dd></dl>
